{"tid":1638341,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"律師: 777未可以動用到緊急法","createTime":"2019-10-08T09:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T10:02:22.000Z","uid":62011,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a1217ee7fc1e784e74761f505bb65f9aa9ce0ad2","tid":1638341,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:33:30.000Z","msg":"律師朋友提醒前線：小心唔好中林鄭詭計<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n//其實777知佢仲未可以動用到緊急法，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但佢特登令我地自己營造緊急打仗狀態，到司法覆核既時候佢既律師就可以同法庭講 &ldquo;係呀之前都可能未justified 但依家就唔同啦&rdquo; </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n星期五第一個司法覆核就係咁輸<br />\n<br />\n岩岩今日入court 個份係本世紀最強既律師團一齊整，真係寫得好好，但如果我地又自己搞到打仗咁就完全幫緊林太。<br />\n<br />\n如果呢個覆核成功，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">成條緊急法都會被廢除</span></strong>，個盒唔會再有人有得玩。//<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n今日休息下，俾和理非/大律師做野，我地絕不割蓆不篤灰，今日係做國際文宣，比外媒影相，今日唔裝唔放火。最尾衰左，前線先出手！</span>(呢句我未敢認同)<br />\n<br />\n高院受理左司法覆核，一定要同律師同一陣線，唔好俾機會政府！<br />\n<br />\n消息來源: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aa9h7B5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAa9h7B5.png&h=f3013dab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n我既觀點:<br />\n1. 政府過去三日先叫黨鐵、連鎖店提早收工。今日就叫黨鐵、診所、大學提早收工，連鎖店唔知有無。好可能逐步營造戒嚴氣氛。同上面所講好合理。<br />\n<br />\n2. 死差佬會派人搞破壞，配合政府。<br />\n<br />\n破解: 大型行動會俾道理政府推緊急法，唔行動政府又話緊急法成功。所以我建議大家營造一個緊急但又唔緊急既氣氛，陰中有陽，陽中有陰。將政府帶返入尷尬地位。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f04dbbfd625e69b8d85f0f1458f2fb8ac75552c","tid":1638341,"uid":154012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:37:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c32b388cc528f13d7e70fa13c6f8dbd028581dc3","tid":1638341,"uid":73915,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:38:03.000Z","msg":"點呀律師朋友<br />\n使唔使勇武退場，你先上到庭？"},{"pid":"7a767056f5d3910cb51737d262a5838ff8a16f42","tid":1638341,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:38:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19a4d15ac367dfba53c4c8783c56542ee6a84532","tid":1638341,"uid":104816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:38:55.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"8e8d53b44620d1e1b795a9727616e10013afdcb9","tid":1638341,"uid":130695,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:38:57.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，律師朋友，美國朋友，你老母閪未生出黎既朋友"},{"pid":"b8895913a19072a2bc2954f3df5310e6c588ccaf","tid":1638341,"uid":73915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:39:16.000Z","msg":"講咁撚耐一個律師名都未有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1bf369acb0364bb69c067eb5c76c6170f014f7c","tid":1638341,"uid":315851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:39:56.000Z","msg":"因為行街唔係集會，唔觸發蒙面法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班狗唔係咁睇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af08d8dd9b8356cd258c0912b0e89c9aaf7d8bf","tid":1638341,"uid":151966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1217ee7fc1e784e74761f505bb65f9aa9ce0ad2","tid":1638341,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:33:30.000Z","msg":"律師朋友提醒前線：小心唔好中林鄭詭計<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n//其實777知佢仲未可以動用到緊急法，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但佢特登令我地自己營造緊急打仗狀態，到司法覆核既時候佢既律師就可以同法庭講 &ldquo;係呀之前都可能未justified 但依家就唔同啦&rdquo; </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n星期五第一個司法覆核就係咁輸<br />\n<br />\n岩岩今日入court 個份係本世紀最強既律師團一齊整，真係寫得好好，但如果我地又自己搞到打仗咁就完全幫緊林太。<br />\n<br />\n如果呢個覆核成功，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">成條緊急法都會被廢除</span></strong>，個盒唔會再有人有得玩。//<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n今日休息下，俾和理非/大律師做野，我地絕不割蓆不篤灰，今日係做國際文宣，比外媒影相，今日唔裝唔放火。最尾衰左，前線先出手！</span>(呢句我未敢認同)<br />\n<br />\n高院受理左司法覆核，一定要同律師同一陣線，唔好俾機會政府！<br />\n<br />\n消息來源: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aa9h7B5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAa9h7B5.png&h=f3013dab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n我既觀點:<br />\n1. 政府過去三日先叫黨鐵、連鎖店提早收工。今日就叫黨鐵、診所、大學提早收工，連鎖店唔知有無。好可能逐步營造戒嚴氣氛。同上面所講好合理。<br />\n<br />\n2. 死差佬會派人搞破壞，配合政府。<br />\n<br />\n破解: 大型行動會俾道理政府推緊急法，唔行動政府又話緊急法成功。所以我建議大家營造一個緊急但又唔緊急既氣氛，陰中有陽，陽中有陰。將政府帶返入尷尬地位。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:40:27.000Z","msg":"係啦係啦咁多朋友"},{"pid":"cb6d1c7ea9c35a1919fc4cb428ce40e8e1dd3341","tid":1638341,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:41:19.000Z","msg":"（廣傳！推上國際！港共政權公然欺騙立法會和聯合國！）在1999年9月立法會民政事務委員會特別會議上，特區政府回應16個非政府機構對香港參照《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》所提交報告的意見，明言：「在緊急情況下根據《緊急情況規例條例》制定的規例&hellip;&hellip;都是附屬法例，因此必須通過立法會的審核程序」「Regulations that could be made in emergencies under the Emergency Regulations Ordinance will have to be consistent with Article 4 of the ICCPR. Such regulations would be subsidiary legislation and therefore subject to vetting by the Legislative Council.」<br />\n<br />\n相同說法於下一個月寫入交給聯合國人權事務委員會的補充資料。這些材料雖然不具備法律約束力，但若特區政府藉着《緊急法》繞過立法會制定附例，便等於承認過去公開欺騙立法會、聯合國和其他相關組織。<br />\n<br />\n是誰一再破壞香港法治精神？政府99年話「保證」「一定」「必須」等字眼，今日就一秒間推反，強行引用《緊急法》!<br />\n<br />\n中文：<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr98-99/chinese/panels/ha/papers/ha2309_2.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr98-99%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Fha%2Fpapers%2Fha2309_2.htm&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNtagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=3e5ab367\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr98-99/chinese/panels/ha/papers/ha2309_2.htm</a><br />\n<br />\nEnglish ：<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr98-99/english/panels/ha/papers/ha2309_2.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr98-99%2Fenglish%2Fpanels%2Fha%2Fpapers%2Fha2309_2.htm&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNtagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=56c52535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr98-99/english/panels/ha/papers/ha2309_2.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qHR4NH8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqHR4NH8.png&h=432f8efa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=136224777720313&amp;id=110776013598523&amp;_ft_=mf_story_key.136224777720313%3Atop_level_post_id.136224777720313%3Atl_objid.136224777720313%3Acontent_owner_id_new.110776013598523%3Athrowback_story_fbid.136224777720313%3Apage_id.110776013598523%3Aphoto_id.136233711052753%3Astory_location.4%3Astory_attachment_style.photo%3Apage_insights.%7B%22110776013598523%22%3A%7B%22page_id%22%3A110776013598523%2C%22actor_id%22%3A110776013598523%2C%22dm%22%3A%7B%22isShare%22%3A0%2C%22originalPostOwnerID%22%3A0%7D%2C%22psn%22%3A%22EntStatusCreationStory%22%2C%22post_context%22%3A%7B%22object_fbtype%22%3A266%2C%22publish_time%22%3A1570181962%2C%22story_name%22%3A%22EntStatusCreationStory%22%2C%22story_fbid%22%3A%5B136224777720313%5D%7D%2C%22role%22%3A1%2C%22sl%22%3A4%2C%22targets%22%3A%5B%7B%22actor_id%22%3A110776013598523%2C%22page_id%22%3A110776013598523%2C%22post_id%22%3A136224777720313%2C%22role%22%3A1%2C%22share_id%22%3A0%7D%5D%7D%7D&amp;__tn__=%2As%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D136224777720313%26id%3D110776013598523%26_ft_%3Dmf_story_key.136224777720313%253Atop_level_post_id.136224777720313%253Atl_objid.136224777720313%253Acontent_owner_id_new.110776013598523%253Athrowback_story_fbid.136224777720313%253Apage_id.110776013598523%253Aphoto_id.136233711052753%253Astory_location.4%253Astory_attachment_style.photo%253Apage_insights.%257B%2522110776013598523%2522%253A%257B%2522page_id%2522%253A110776013598523%252C%2522actor_id%2